            <description><![CDATA[【🤧<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E6%B5%81%E6%84%9F%E5%90%8E%E5%90%83%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E7%8E%9B%E5%B7%B4%E6%B4%9B%E6%B2%99%E9%9F%A6%E5%B0%B1%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E6%B5%81%E6%84%9F%E5%90%8E%E5%90%83%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E7%8E%9B%E5%B7%B4%E6%B4%9B%E6%B2%99%E9%9F%A6%E5%B0%B1%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#感染流感后吃一次玛巴洛沙韦就有效#</span></a> 】专家表示，对于轻症流感，玛巴洛沙韦服用1次即可，或服用奥司他韦，每天早晚各1粒，吃5天。非重症人群不建议同时服用两种药👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%B5%81%E6%84%9F%E5%8F%91%E7%97%85%E7%9A%8448%E5%B0%8F%E6%97%B6%E6%98%AF%E8%87%AA%E6%95%91%E9%BB%84%E9%87%91%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%B5%81%E6%84%9F%E5%8F%91%E7%97%85%E7%9A%8448%E5%B0%8F%E6%97%B6%E6%98%AF%E8%87%AA%E6%95%91%E9%BB%84%E9%87%91%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#流感发病的48小时是自救黄金时间#</span></a> （CCTV生活圈）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4995665554767884" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">CCTV生活圈的微博视频</span></a> <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/orj480/713e54f1ly1hmaxe0kdv7j21hc0u0di2.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/V4fANIVflx08c85WonpC01041200dw440E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1706620879&amp;ssig=B2efyS5w%2BI&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/RRxn8BM5lx08c85VTV0s010412006Ek10E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1706620879&amp;ssig=YmQzXCW9JT&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/x7C5TXOhlx08c85VTouk010