        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[[裂开]#6种症状提醒你该查血脂了# 根据《中国血脂管理指南（2023 年）》显示，中国成人血脂异常总体患病率已经高达35.6%！长期患高脂血症可致动脉粥样硬化，增加...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[裂开]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/fc_liekai-9df295d44f.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%236%E7%A7%8D%E7%97%87%E7%8A%B6%E6%8F%90%E9%86%92%E4%BD%A0%E8%AF%A5%E6%9F%A5%E8%A1%80%E8%84%82%E4%BA%86%23&amp;extparam=%236%E7%A7%8D%E7%97%87%E7%8A%B6%E6%8F%90%E9%86%92%E4%BD%A0%E8%AF%A5%E6%9F%A5%E8%A1%80%E8%84%82%E4%BA%86%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#6种症状提醒你该查血脂了#</span></a> 根据《中国血脂管理指南（2023 年）》显示，中国成人血脂异常总体患病率已经高达35.6%！长期患高脂血症可致动脉粥样硬化，增加心血管疾病的发病率和死亡率。出现以下6个症状，提醒你该查血脂了👇🏻<br><br><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[星星]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/_/x_star1-e5d754c7b6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>头晕犯困：时常头晕头痛、胸闷气短、睡眠不好等；清晨头脑不清醒，午后易犯困，夜晚却很清醒。<br><br><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[星星]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/_/x_star1-e5d754c7b6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>眼球周边有灰白环：黑眼球边缘被一圈灰白色圆环或弧形半圆环包围，颜色会随着时间不断加深且越来越明显。<br><br><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[星星]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/_/x_star1-e5d754c7b6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>手部有黄色结节：手背、指关节等部位出现黄色、橘黄色或棕红色的斑块或疹子，或手掌出现黄色或橘黄色条纹。<br><br><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[星星]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/_/x_star1-e5d754c7b6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>腿肚抽筋：腿脚经常抽筋、刺痛，补钙，休息却并无好转。<br><br><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[星星]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/_/x_star1-e5d754c7b6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>视力模糊：血液中的甘油三酯增多、流速减缓，脂蛋白从毛细血管露出且侵犯到黄斑，就会影响视力。<br><br><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[星星]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/_/x_star1-e5d754c7b6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>黄色瘤：眼皮、胳膊肘、脚后跟等部位，长出米粒大小的黄色瘤。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（健康广东）<img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hmbg5x27yqg20g60azkjl.gif" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
            <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 02:32:29 GMT</pubDate>
